data.description: Unique one of a kind Rainbow Springs home with 2918 square feet. This is a 3 bedroom 2.5 bath pool home sitting on .41 acres in the Rainbow Springs Country Club. This home has vaulted ceilings with large rustic wood beams. The entrance is tiled with a wood railing matching the ceiling beams. Oversized, living room with floor to ceiling wood burning fireplace and floor to ceiling windows. There is also a full bar area with sink and wine cooler. Living area has an open concept with a great kitchen for entertaining. You will not have your back to your guests because the cooktop is located in the island facing the living room and your guests. The bedrooms are all large and spacious with plenty of closet space. One guest room has built in office space in the closet. The guest rooms also have access to the Jack and Jill bathroom separating them. There is also a half bath for guests centrally located for when your entertaining. The home has a deck that sits above the pool area for a birds eye view of the beautiful green space. Step down into the pool area which has all been redone in 2017. Pool Is salt water and has beautiful pavers all around. The pool area has that tropic feel with 4 palm trees located in the corner of the pool area. The area also has built in privacy with a 4 foot block stucco wall built around the pool area. This home has a 2 car attached garage with plenty of parking and a circle drive for easy access to the home. The neighborhood also has low HOA fees and access to the highly sought after rainbow river and the community center with a pool and fitness center.
